commit.message: added a BONUS to my challenge - added Facebook support. Now we're getting videos from Facebook pages
added more params to YouTube search to try more precision
added support to navigate between videos through arrow keys and close using esc key
added play icon over thumbnails and added simple icons to chrome extension portal
added header and disclaimer to the box and also fixed a bug on video opening
removed an not necessary request from yt api
added preload images on hidden videos waiting for pagination click in order to avoid blinks in pagination transition
added action to open video in a modal
added the pagination with carrousel following the Yelp's style guide
initial commit with a base extension
